text: The Anglo-Manipur War or the Anglo-Manipuri War was a war between the British Empire and the Manipur kingdom. The war started on March 31, 1891 and ended on April 27, 1891 with a British victory.http://archivesmanipur.nic.in/whoswho.htm ==Related pages== * Tikendrajit Singh * Ethel Grimwood ==References== Category:Wars involving the British Empire Category:History of Manipur Category:1890s in Asia Category:1891 Category:19th-century conflicts Category:Wars involving Asia
